---
const faqs = [
  {
    question: 'Who is Speke built for?',
    answer: 'Speke is designed for enterprises and established companies running distributed teams that need both structured text communication and instant voice collaboration.'
  },
  {
    question: 'How is this different from email and traditional chat tools?',
    answer: 'Speke keeps written communication organized in one place and adds instant voice conversations when teams need quick alignment, so work moves faster without losing context.'
  },
  {
    question: 'Does each company get a private workspace boundary?',
    answer: 'Yes. The product is built around organization-level isolation so each company operates in its own workspace context.'
  },
  {
    question: 'Can teams onboard quickly?',
    answer: 'Yes. Teams can create organizations, define channels, assign member roles, and bring people in through invite links and invitations.'
  },
  {
    question: 'What is available right now?',
    answer: 'The live app already includes text channels, call channels, presence indicators, real-time messaging, and organization management. The current site is collecting pilot teams for launch feedback.'
  }
];
---

<section class="section" id="faq">
  <div class="shell">
    <div class="section-heading reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow">FAQ</p>
      <h2>Questions from IT and operations teams</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-list">
      {faqs.map((item) => (
        <details class="faq-item reveal">
          <summary>{item.question}</summary>
          <p>{item.answer}</p>
        </details>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
